description: You’ll find a ton of El Guajillo fans in Houston. Once you taste this marvelous cuisine straight from Morelia, Mexico, you’ll understand why. Their menu features beautifully vibrant and flavorful eats, like Pambazo, Chilaquiles, Enchiladas, and tacos with your choice of pork, chicken, or beef. Locals love this wonderfully fresh fare, so you’ll have to come on down to El Guajillo because they’re serving the most delicious Mexican food around.
name: El Guajillo
